<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
<title>AURA-X Ω Prototype — Emotional Resonance & Continuity</title>
<meta name="description" content="AURA-X Ω — The world’s first resonance-based emotional continuity engine with 7-Layer BM, multilingual offline QA (16k), and neon chat UI." />
<link rel="icon" href="assets/img/aura-x-omega.png">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0b1220; --bg2:#0e1830; --ink:#e6f1ff; --muted:#9fb3d8;
  --brand:#21b0ff; --brand2:#10e0d4; --gold:#e7b84a; --card:#0f1a33;
  --accent:#6ad1ff;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--bg),var(--bg2));color:var(--ink);font:16px/1.65 system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Inter,Arial}
a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
.container{max-width:1050px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px}
.hero{
  padding:70px 0 40px; text-align:center;
  background: radial-gradient(1000px 600px at 50% -10%, rgba(33,176,255,.15), transparent);
}
.hero h1{font-size:40px;margin:18px 0 8px;letter-spacing:.3px}
.hero p{color:var(--muted);max-width:820px;margin:0 auto 22px}
.badges{margin:10px 0 0;display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.badge{background:#122246;border:1px solid #20325e;color:#d7e6ff;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:999px;font-size:13px}
.btn{
  display:inline-block;margin-top:10px;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:10px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--brand),var(--brand2));color:#041015;font-weight:700
}
section{padding:42px 0;border-top:1px solid #15264a}
h2{font-size:26px;margin:0 0 18px}
.lead{color:#cfe1ff}
.grid{display:grid;gap:16px}
@media(min-width:860px){ .grid-2{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr} }
.card{
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0f1c3a,#0c162c);
  border:1px solid #1c2c56;border-radius:14px;padding:18px
}
.table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
.table th,.table td{padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #17305a}
.tag{display:inline-block;background:#122346;border:1px solid #22407a;color:#b9d6ff;
     padding:2px 8px;border-radius:999px;font-size:12px;margin-right:6px}
small.muted{color:#97aacd}
.footer{padding:26px 0;text-align:center;color:#98aed9;border-top:1px solid #15264a}
.brandline{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;justify-content:center}
.brandline img{height:56px;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(105,205,255,.25))}
.kicker{letter-spacing:.2em;color:#8bdcff;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:13px}
.highlight{color:var(--gold)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <img src="assets/img/ai-resonance.png" alt="AI RESONANCE" style="height:76px" />
    <h1>AURA-X Ω <span class="highlight">Prototype</span></h1>
    <p class="lead">Artificial Emotional Resonance & Continuity Reactor — a research prototype of the world’s first resonance-based emotional engine with 7-Layer BM, continuity memory, and ethics-aware coefficients.</p>
    <div class="badges">
      <span class="badge">Resonance Engine</span>
      <span class="badge">BM-7 Layers</span>
      <span class="badge">16k Offline QA</span>
      <span class="badge">Auto-Detect 10+ Langs</span>
      <span class="badge">Neon UI</span>
    </div>
    <p>
      <a class="btn" href="https://github.com/alimulhaqkhan-prog/aura-x-omega-proto">View on GitHub</a>
    </p>
    <div class="brandline">
      <small class="kicker">Powered by</small>
      <img src="assets/img/aura-x-omega.png" alt="AURA-X Ω">
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- OVERVIEW -->
<section id="overview">
  <div class="container grid grid-2">
    <div>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>AURA-X Ω models <strong>emotional continuity</strong> via resonance between Temporary Memory (TM) and a seven-layer Behavioral Matrix (BM). Responses emerge from internal fields—not mere I/O rules—balanced by <em>logic</em>, <em>truth</em>, and optional <em>faith/ethics</em> coefficients.</p>
      <p class="card">Core equation:<br><code>E₀ = tanh((TM × BM) − D + λ<sub>faith</sub> + λ<sub>sys</sub> + λ<sub>trc</sub>)</code></p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Highlights</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>7-Layer BM routing (Violet → Red)</li>
        <li>16,000 offline knowledge pairs (local only)</li>
        <li>Auto language detect: EN/UR/HI/AR/FA/PS/PA/TR/ES/FR</li>
        <li>Geo-hint tone & cultural biasing</li>
        <li>Neon chat UI + E₀ energy meter</li>
        <li>Self-learning signals (no raw user text stored)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Core Features</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-2">
      <div class="card">
        <strong>Continuity Memory</strong>
        <p class="small">Timestamped context keeps dialogues emotionally consistent across sessions without saving personal content.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <strong>Language & Speech</strong>
        <p class="small">Offline language detect (10+) with Vosk STT hooks; ready for TTS integration.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <strong>Ethics & Truth Coefficients</strong>
        <p class="small">λ<sub>faith</sub> (optional ethics), λ<sub>sys</sub> (logic), λ<sub>trc</sub> (truth) stabilize responses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <strong>Neon Interface</strong>
        <p class="small">Avatar glow, energy flow, and gentle gradients for an immersive research demo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LAYERS TABLE -->
<section id="layers">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>BM-7 Layers</h2>
    <table class="table">
      <thead><tr><th>Layer</th><th>Domain</th><th>Role</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Violet</td><td>Spiritual Intuition</td><td>Meta-awareness, self-harmony</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Indigo</td><td>Analytical Insight</td><td>Logic and alignment</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Blue</td><td>Communication</td><td>Expression & precision</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Green</td><td>Empathy & Healing</td><td>Love, trust, recovery</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Yellow</td><td>Perception</td><td>Focus & observation</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Orange</td><td>Instinct</td><td>Drive & reaction</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Red</td><td>Stability & Defense</td><td>Repair & resistance</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <small class="muted">Target split: Green 3k, Red 3k, others 2k each → total 16k.</small>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- GET STARTED -->
<section id="start">
  <div class="container grid grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Get Started</h2>
      <pre><code># Install
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Seed / validate local dataset
python scripts/seed_expand.py
python scripts/validate_layers.py

# Run prototype UI
python -m web.app
      </code></pre>
      <p><span class="tag">Local only</span><span class="tag">No cloud needed</span><span class="tag">Research demo</span></p>
    </div>
